&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Partner across teams. &lt;/strong&gt;You&#39;ll work closely with the CEO and other members of the Executive and Senior Leadership Team, as well as cross-functional stakeholders and board members, to ensure clear communication and well-organized logistics.&lt;/li&gt;
