&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You’ll Partner With:&lt;/strong&gt; You’ll work in close collaboration with your dedicated quad (Product Designer, Product Manager, Engineering Manager, Product Marketing Manager) and serve as a bridge between various product teams to ensure design consistency across the platform.&lt;/li&gt;
