&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience: &lt;/strong&gt;Significant experience in product design, specifically managing complex information architecture and B2B/Enterprise workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Design Systems Ownership:&lt;/strong&gt; Proven experience maintaining and evolving design systems, including the ability to delegate design tasks and collaborate with Engineering on implementation.&lt;/li&gt;
